            <h2 class="decorated">Identity Overview</h2>
            <p class="lead">How can we make your Hub reflect your brand?</p>

            <p>In the following section we will present the various Hub pages mentioned before and articulate how and where we can accommodate your unique brand requirements.</p>
            <p>This can include anything from logos and colours, to journal covers and key graphics or imagery.</p>
            <p>However, it is important to be aware that a well thought out identity does not stop at the logos and colours shown on a website. It persists through the style of writing, the name and URL of the site, the style of photography, and many other aspects.</p>

            <p><strong>Some aspects of your Hub you may want to consider early in the process include:</strong></p>
