        <a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-identity" href="#identity3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="identity3">
          Imagery
        </a>
      </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="identity3" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingThree">
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            <p>Most of the imagery throughout the Hub will be directly connected to journals, issues and articles. However, there may be opportunities to showcase important events, featured issues or highlighted articles. In these situations, using an interesting, brand related image can reinforce the Hub identity and encourage more views.
                            </p>
                        </div>
